<HEADLINE> 5 Killed, 16 Injured in Road Accident </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 18 (Xinhua) -- Five persons were killed and
sixteen others injured on Friday in a road accident between a
truck and a bus at Thapla Kharian, Punjab Province, police
officials said.
</P>
<P>
The truck was on its way to Lahore from Rawalpindi when it
reached at Thapla Kharian while the bus came from behind, hitting
the truck and overturned.
</P>
<P>
Five persons died on the spot while sixteen others were injured.
</P>
</TEXT>
