The annual event, which is scheduled to open September 23, has
set up 80 booths for the trading of feature films and TV play.
</P>
<P>
Sources at the festival's organizing committee said, 110
Chinese and overseas films will go through the best-film selection
process. They include 88 films in Chinese, and 22 from the United
States, France, Japan and Russia.
</P>
<P>
