<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, August 18 (Xinhua) -- Venezuelan President Hugo Chavez
called on Friday the Andean countries to speed up the integration
process in America, especially the Latin American integration in
economic, social, cultural and political fields.
</P>
<P>
Chavez made the remarks during the inauguration of an
extraordinary meeting of the Andean Integration System. He asked
the countries to make efforts for the unification process, but not
be limited to the "economic or technical" level.
</P>
