<HEADLINE> Chinese Disabled Win Four Gold Medals in Prague </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, August 18 (Xinhua) -- The 5th international
professional skills competition for the disabled has wound up here
Friday, from which Chinese contestants garnered four gold medals
in embroidery, batiking, knotting and dress making.
</P>
